      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S5LV0663P0_20040713_GCR_123'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-elizabeth-barker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0663P0_20040713_GCR_123' title='Link to this speech by Ms Elizabeth Barker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-elizabeth-barker" title="Ms Elizabeth Barker">Baroness Barker</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Perhaps the noble Baroness could use the letter she said she will write to answer another, similar question. How much time will there be between a non-compliance event and the issue of a contribution notice? No time limits are specified anywhere in the clause.
          </p>
